Hello, my name is Supreeth.
I am a Data Scientist, researching and developing machine learning products with RozieAI.
I have over 8 years of experience in the field of Data Science and building scalable ML/AI products is my competence. I am a Microsoft Certified: Azure Data Scientist Associate with professional working experience in Azure and AWS.
I am currently focusing on learning, experimenting and building Generative AI solutions.
This website is my canvas where I share everything I learn and experiment with.
